成立，或問題可以解決就可以，唔需要論證 「百利而無一害」<br />\n（反正我亦見唔到你有好充分嘅理據咁講，只係以《中庸》一句，就想當然）<br />\n（而且，世事唔一定係人人想安分守己就冇問題，<br />\n好多時何謂安分，都大有討論空間）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己參考下，我唔識俾分，會考年代作文拎A"},{"pid":"55c0678a0e3d8bed3704be4e3cd248ca9861b753","tid":615089,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12f8056b44d15942ed914cc357884ceaf4b31a15","tid":615089,"uid":35190,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"成篇似係《論中庸》更多，而非論處世。<br />\n正如論情感變左論開心咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既然講得中庸，仲有狂者、狷者、鄉愿呢幾種處世態度都可以做比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，最後亦可反思係現代中庸是否仲做得到？定已經陳義太高？或者應對唔同事先有唔同既處世模式？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有捉得緊既marker可能會kill左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外整個框架較為死板，難上星"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"徐巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會改善 嘗試套落現代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82e7b4f02108c19b88709e62832cb92ece2b484","tid":615089,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"如果我睇左幾百篇差唔多既野<br />\n再改你呢篇，最多拎3<br />\n<br />\n睇到恰眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無乜特別既論證方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad87650cfe3605ddbca6f182e368c6b51130665d","tid":615089,"uid":126973,"